## 2. Test Strategy

### 2.1 Test Levels

|  |  |  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Level | Abbreviation | Purpose | Automation | Server Coverage |
| Property-Based Testing | PBT | Verify invariants hold for random inputs | 100% automated | Node.js only (fast-check) |
| Unit Testing | UT | Verify individual class/function behavior | 100% automated | All 3 servers |
| Integration Testing | IT | Verify component interactions with real SQLite | 100% automated | All 3 servers |
| End-to-End API Testing | E2E-API | Verify MCP tool calls via stdio protocol | 100% automated | All 3 servers |
| End-to-End UI Testing | E2E-UI | N/A — no UI in this system | N/A | N/A |
| System Integration Testing | SIT | Verify cross-server compatibility & migration | 90% automated, 10% manual | Cross-server |

**Note:** E2E-UI is not applicable for this ticket as the system is a headless MCP server with no user interface. All interaction is via MCP protocol (JSON-RPC over stdio).

### 2.2 Test Approach per Feature

|  |  |  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Feature | PBT Focus | UT Focus | IT Focus | E2E-API Focus |
| F1: Core Memory | Token counting invariants, budget never exceeded | CoreMemoryManager methods | Pin + search integration | mem\_pin tool all actions |
| F2: Conversation | Turn ordering invariants | ConversationRepo methods | Save + query + summarize | mem\_conversation tool all actions |
| F3: Structured Map | Entity extraction patterns | StructuredMapExtractor, EntityClassifier | Ingest + extract + index | mem\_map tool all actions |
| F4: Anti-Pattern | Quality score bounds [0,100] | QualityGate, AgentScopeFilter, TokenBudget, WorkingTierExpiry | Full search pipeline with all F4 components | Enhanced mem\_search + mem\_ingest |

### 2.3 Test Environment

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Environment | Purpose | Configuration |
| Local Dev | Unit + Integration tests | SQLite in-memory, ONNX model loaded |
| CI (GitHub Actions) | Automated test suite | SQLite temp file, all 3 servers |
| Staging | E2E-API + SIT | Real SQLite file, full MCP protocol |

### 2.4 Test Data Strategy

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Data Type | Source | Management |
| Knowledge entries | Generated fixtures (50-5000 chars) | CSV seed files |
| Conversation turns | Predefined sessions (5-100 turns) | JSON fixtures |
| Entity patterns | Curated regex test cases | CSV with expected classifications |
| Quality gate inputs | Edge cases (49 chars, 50 chars, duplicates) | Inline test data |
| Agent scope configs | Default 5 roles + custom | JSON fixtures |

