| 7 | Test data prepared | Fixtures and seed data ready |

### 4.2 Exit Criteria

|  |  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| # | Criterion | Target | Measurement |
| 1 | All Critical test cases pass | 100% | TC execution report |
| 2 | All High priority test cases pass | ≥95% | TC execution report |
| 3 | Code coverage ≥80% | ≥80% lines | Coverage tool output |
| 4 | No Critical/High severity defects open | 0 | Defect tracker |
| 5 | Performance targets met | All within spec | Benchmark results |
| 6 | Regression tests pass | 100% | Existing test suite |
| 7 | All 3 servers produce consistent results | 100% parity | Cross-server comparison |

### 4.3 Suspension Criteria

|  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- |
| # | Criterion | Action |
| 1 | >3 Critical defects found in same feature | Suspend testing, return to DEV |
| 2 | Test environment unstable | Suspend until environment fixed |
| 3 | Schema migration fails | Suspend all tests, investigate |

